data.description:
Seller will pay up to $10,000.00 for the BUYERS interest point BUY DOWN!!


This beautiful home is ready for some new owners! There is space for EVERYONE and then some! This massive house has three living areas, yes I said THREE living areas AND a MEDIA ROOM! Not only do you have lots of entertainment space, you can also use one of the bedrooms downstairs as a mother in law suite. The basement has a full wet bar and it's right next to the media room! Don't worry, the 5 ft deep Swim Spa/Pool will be staying so you can enjoy it all year long! If you are wanting views of the Bookcliffs, you will not be disappointed.This home is priced to sell, don't miss out! Call for a private showing. Buyer to verify all information.
